name: Juno Eclipse, Black Leader
Lore: 'A shining example of Imperial honor and bravery. Female.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything she pilots.  Deploys -1 to starships.  Naboo Blaster is a matching weapon for her.  While with Galen at a site, adds one battle destiny.  During your control phase, may use 2 Force to retrieve a card with ''back'' in title.  Immune to attrition < 3.',
